{"id":277837,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-江苏上访维权者陆菊华等8人被非法拘禁后/","date":"2013-02-04T21:45:50Z","modified":"2013-02-04T21:45:50Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏上访维权者陆菊华等8人被非法拘禁后获释（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）江苏常州的上访维权者陆菊华、朱玉妹于昨天２月３日早上６点许，从北京至常州的火车下车后，在常州市火车站门口被数名不明身份人绑架至常州新北区的星月宾馆软禁。两人发现同时还有６人也被软禁在一起，都是常州附近的上访维权人士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陆菊华、朱玉妹两人先后被隔离问话，了解关于一元劳教案在北京上访的情况并警告她们今后少上访少给当地政府找麻烦等等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>２月３日下午７点半点左右，陆菊华获释。２月４日中午约１点朱玉妹也被释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>２月４日晚１８：００，本网信息员致电陆菊华询问得知，在常州新北区星月宾馆被非法拘禁的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名上访维权人士已经全部获释，只是她和朱玉妹都不知其他人的姓名与电话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，陆菊华、朱玉妹和吴产娣都是一元劳教案的受害者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>事件起因：２００９年６月，陆菊华、朱玉妹等三人在北京上访，常州警方仅凭公交车司机崔林一个人投诉称逃票</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>元，同年１０月２１日，常州市劳动教养委员会名义作出《劳动教养决定书》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span>（常）劳教委决字（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">508</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span>，对朱玉妹劳教１年。２０１０年４月１２日对陆菊华做出劳教决定书</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span>（常）劳教委决字（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">218</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span>，劳教</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陆菊华手机：１５９６１１０８８７５</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>朱玉妹手机：１５９６１１２５９２３</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图：中间为陆菊华、右为朱玉妹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ua25dCVfpow/UQ_akt7PxiI/AAAAAAAAbWI/KN4lZuafYf4/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"208\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ua25dCVfpow/UQ_akt7PxiI/AAAAAAAAbWI/KN4lZuafYf4/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}